# Xenia Portfolio - Cursor Configuration

## Project Overview
This is a React + Vite portfolio website for Xenia Snapiro. The project uses:
- React 19 with JSX
- Vite as the build tool
- GSAP for animations (optional, can be lazy-loaded)
- ESLint for code quality
- Responsive images (AVIF/WebP format with multiple sizes: 300w, 500w, 800w, 1000w)

